    {"@type":"Question","name":"How much does a new roof cost in Clearwater?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A roof replacement in Clearwater typically costs between $8,000 and $25,000+ depending on roof size, pitch, material selection, and structural repairs. Beachside homes on Clearwater Beach or Sand Key may require enhanced wind-mitigation features due to higher wind-speed zones. Happy Roof provides free, detailed estimates - call (813) 595-7663."}},
