    {"@type":"Question","name":"Does Happy Roof handle Clearwater building permits?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We handle all permit applications with the City of Clearwater and Pinellas County building departments. Our team manages the entire permitting and inspection process from start to finish - you never have to visit a government office."}},
    {"@type":"Question","name":"How quickly can Happy Roof start a project in Clearwater?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"After your free inspection and estimate approval, most Clearwater projects begin within 1 to 3 weeks depending on permit processing times and material availability. Emergency storm damage repairs are prioritized and typically begin within 24 to 48 hours."}},
