<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Happy Roof in Clearwater</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY CLEARWATER HOMEOWNERS CHOOSE HAPPY ROOF</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          Clearwater stretches from the pristine barrier island beaches of Clearwater Beach and Sand Key through the mainland neighborhoods of Countryside, Harbor Oaks, and Clearwater East - each presenting distinct roofing needs. Beachside properties endure constant salt spray that tests every fastener and sealant, while inland homes face the same intense UV radiation and heavy summer rainfall patterns that challenge roofs across all of upper Pinellas County. Finding a roofing contractor who understands these conditions and can navigate the City of Clearwater's permitting requirements is essential.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          Happy Roof has earned the trust of Clearwater homeowners through transparent communication, detailed written estimates, and consistently clean job sites. We hold Florida Roofing Contractor License #CCC1337380, carry full general liability and workers' compensation insurance, and handle every permit and inspection. Whether your home is near the Clearwater Marine Aquarium, along the Courtney Campbell Causeway, or in the established neighborhoods near Countryside Mall, we deliver the same quality - protected by a 15-year workmanship warranty in writing.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6"><div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Owens Corning Installer</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We install premium Owens Corning roofing systems with manufacturer warranties on all products.</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="scard p-6"><div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">15-Year Workmanship Warranty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every Clearwater roof installation includes a written 15-year workmanship warranty. No exceptions.</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="scard p-6"><div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">City of Clearwater Permits Handled</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We manage all permit applications and coordinate inspections with the City of Clearwater and Pinellas County.</p></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

