        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Wind-lifted shingles, cracked tiles, deteriorating flashing, and leak diagnosis - we handle all residential roof repairs across Clearwater. We provide honest assessments and never recommend a full replacement when a targeted repair will solve the problem.</p>
      </div>
