        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4"/><polyline points="16 17 21 12 16 7"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="9" y2="12"/></svg></div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Storm Damage & Insurance</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Clearwater's Gulf-front position makes it especially vulnerable to tropical storms and hurricanes. We provide thorough post-storm damage assessments, document everything for your insurance claim, and work directly with your adjuster to ensure a smooth process.</p>
