      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5"><div class="step-num">1</div><div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Free Inspection & Estimate</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">A thorough inspection of your roof's decking, underlayment, flashing, ventilation, and overall condition. You receive a detailed written estimate with material options, timelines, and transparent pricing.</p></div></div>
