      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5"><div class="step-num">3</div><div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Professional Installation</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Full tear-off, decking inspection and repair, new underlayment and flashing, and installation of your new roofing system to manufacturer specifications. We protect your property throughout the process.</p></div></div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5"><div class="step-num">4</div><div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Final Inspection & Warranty</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">County inspection for code compliance, warranty documentation delivery including our 15-year workmanship warranty, and follow-up at 30 days and 1 year to confirm your satisfaction.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

