    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">Does Happy Roof handle Clearwater building permits?<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. We handle all permit applications with the City of Clearwater and Pinellas County building departments. You never visit a government office - we manage every step from application to final inspection and sign-off.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">How quickly can Happy Roof start a project in Clearwater?<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">After your free inspection and estimate approval, most Clearwater projects begin within 1 to 3 weeks depending on permit processing and material availability. Emergency storm damage repairs are prioritized and typically begin within 24 to 48 hours.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">Is Happy Roof licensed to work in Clearwater?<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. Happy Roof LLC holds Florida Roofing Contractor License #CCC1337380 and is authorized to work throughout all of Florida, including the City of Clearwater and Pinellas County. We carry full general liability and workers' compensation insurance, with certificates available on request.</div></div></div>
